document.topic_text: Photo: Carolyn Kaster, AP Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Clinton greets people as she arrives at Provincetown Municipal Airport in Provincetown, Mass., Sunday, Aug. 21, 2016. Clinton is traveling to a fundraiser at the Pilgrim Monument and Provincetown Museum in Provincetown. Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Clinton greets people as... PROVINCETOWN, Mass. (AP) — It was a very busy, very lucrative weekend for Hillary Clinton in the summer playground of the East Coast's moneyed elite.
